<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<style>
@page { size: A4 portrait; margin: 12mm 12mm 18mm 15mm; }
* { box-sizing: border-box; }
body { font-family: "Noto Sans JP","Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro","MS Gothic",sans-serif; font-size: 9.5pt; color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0; line-height: 1.4; }
.doc-title { font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; border: 2px solid #1a1a1a; padding: 5px 0; margin-bottom: 7px; letter-spacing: 3px; }
table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 6px; }
th, td { border: 1px solid #333; padding: 3px 5px; font-size: 9pt; vertical-align: top; }
th { background: #e8eaf0; font-weight: bold; white-space: nowrap; text-align: center; }
h2 { font-size: 10pt; font-weight: bold; border-left: 4px solid #2563eb; padding: 2px 7px; margin: 8px 0 4px; background: #f0f4ff; }
.weather-icon { font-size: 16pt; text-align: center; }
.stamp-area { display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 8px; margin: 10px 0; }
.stamp-wrap { text-align: center; }
.stamp-box { width: 60px; height: 60px; border: 1px solid #333; font-size: 8pt; padding-top: 3px; }
.stamp-label { font-size: 8pt; margin-top: 2px; }
.doc-footer { margin-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #999; padding-top: 4px; font-size: 8pt; color: #666; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
.center { text-align: center; } .right { text-align: right; }
.note-box { border: 1px solid #999; min-height: 45px; padding: 4px; font-size: 9pt; }
@media print { body { -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="doc-title">工 事 日 誌</div>

<table>
  <tr>
    <th style="width:70px">工 事 名</th><td colspan="5">テスト案件</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>工事番号</th><td style="width:100px">　</td>
    <th style="width:60px">記 入 日</th><td style="width:110px">　　年　　月　　日</td>
    <th style="width:60px">曜 日</th><td style="width:60px">　曜日</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>請 負 者</th><td>　</td>
    <th>現場代理人</th><td colspan="3">　</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h2>天候</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr><th style="width:80px">時 間 帯</th><th style="width:100px">天候</th><th style="width:60px">気温(℃)</th><th style="width:70px">湿度(%)</th><th style="width:70px">風速(m/s)</th><th>作業への影響</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td class="center">午前</td>
      <td class="center">晴</td>
      <td class="center"></td>
      <td class="center"></td>
      <td class="center"></td>
      <td></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="center">午後</td>
      <td class="center">曇</td>
      <td class="center"></td>
      <td class="center"></td>
      <td class="center"></td>
      <td></td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2>作業内容</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="width:100px">工 種</th>
      <th>作業内容</th>
      <th style="width:60px">作業場所</th>
      <th style="width:40px">作業員数</th>
      <th style="width:60px">進捗率(%)</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    
    
    <tr><td>　</td><td>　</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
    
    <tr><td>　</td><td>　</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
    
    <tr><td>　</td><td>　</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
    
    <tr><td>　</td><td>　</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
    
    <tr><td>　</td><td>　</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
    
    <tr><td>　</td><td>　</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
    
    
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2>作業員・機械等</h2>
<table>
  <tr>
    <th style="width:100px">作業員合計</th><td>　 名</td>
    <th style="width:100px">使用機械</th><td>　</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>資材搬入</th><td>　</td>
    <th>搬出</th><td>　</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h2>安全管理</h2>
<table>
  <tr>
    <th style="width:100px">KY活動</th>
    <td style="width:60px">
      □ 未実施
    </td>
    <th style="width:100px">安全朝礼</th>
    <td style="width:60px">
      □ 未実施
    </td>
    <th style="width:100px">安全巡回</th>
    <td>
      □ 未実施
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>事故・ヒヤリ</th>
    <td colspan="5">なし</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h2>指示・連絡事項</h2>
<div class="note-box" style="min-height:40px;"></div>

<h2>特記事項</h2>
<div class="note-box" style="min-height:40px;"></div>

<div class="stamp-area">
  <div class="stamp-wrap"><div class="stamp-box">監督員</div><div class="stamp-label">監督員</div></div>
  <div class="stamp-wrap"><div class="stamp-box">現場代理人</div><div class="stamp-label">現場代理人</div></div>
  <div class="stamp-wrap"><div class="stamp-box">記録者</div><div class="stamp-label">記録者</div></div>
</div>

<div class="doc-footer">
  <span>工事日誌（公共建築工事標準仕様書 令和7年版）</span>
